Goeyers &amp; Van de Vijver
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1027,1118,1559,1585]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
SEM. Campbell Island 
<typeStatus box="[189,292,1594,1620]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">holotype</typeStatus>
population, sample BAS272 (BR-4581). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[778,822,1594,1620]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">132</emphasis>
. Frustule in girdle view with the narrow copulae. The arrows indicate the ligulae. 
